{
  "stem": "1918.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 437.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that it happens perhaps just to some people, to political opponents, but not to ordinary people, to women and children.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's impossible, you know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You would not believe if somebody came with stories like that to you, and you would not think that tomorrow it will happen to you.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it somehow-- we were terrified always because we heard all of this ranting and raving from Hitler.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it wasn't that immediate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It wasn't right in my kitchen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And as a matter of fact, I remember a very particular instance when a cousin of mine, my mother's brother's son, who was involved in trying to save Jews-- he eventually survived-- and he directed a woman, somebody very-- someone who was very important to aid and save.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I believe she was from Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she was to come to my town to the railroad station, and then somebody was to accompany her to a town called, I believe, Debrecen, where my little twin brothers were perished.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, and-- I don't remember the name.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this cousin came to my mother to make the arrangements.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This cousin was a bearded Jew, but he was able to move yet.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this was before-- I believe, before Hitler marched in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he negotiated with my mother for me that I was a teenager, I was ostensibly very presentable looking, and I could pass for a Gentile.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I would accompany this woman to the next town where somebody else would pick her up.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But my orders were not to talk to anyone, and certainly not to talk to the woman.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The woman would be sitting, I don't know, two rows away from me.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
